data.description: Discover a truly one-of-a-kind home at 375 Fairmont Way in Fairburn, GA! This attractive property boasts 4 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, all within a stunning 2,050 sqft of living space. Built in 2008, this house is a rare gem in a highly sought-after neighborhood. You'll love being just minutes away from local attractions, public transportation, and a beautiful public park. The garage and one of the bathrooms need some work, but this house is a diamond of an investment opportunity. This property won't be available for long!
